            },
            {
                "comment": "Most frustrating class I've taken. He emphasizes learning concepts but doesn't teach whatsoever - only 1-2 does example problems per class. Podcasts have little useful information. Quizzes come completely out of left field and are under tight time constraints.",
                "difficulty_rating": 3,
                "quality_rating": 1
