            {
                "comment": "You really have to teach yourself what you're doing using the videos that he posts online. In lecture he works practice problems and makes them look way easier than they really are. He never really teaches concepts and just expects you to know what you are doing. Your midterm & final make up 50% of your grade with weekly quizzes at 20% and labs 30%",
                "difficulty_rating": 5,
                "quality_rating": 2
